                <p>U.S. allocation now authorized permits exportation of 25,000 tons of flour or
                    wheat equivalent in July, to arrive in Brazil in July or August.</p>
                <p>In view of Argentine shipments described below it is obvious that imports from
                    that country are unsatisfactory to Brazil.</p>
                <p rend="center">
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Imports from Argentina</hi>
                </p>
